 Galvatron shook his head. "Five more minutes mommy....um what?" he sat us 
and rubbed his optics. Crawling out of the pits could make a bot tired. He 
staretched and walked over its not hard. If anything come within a few 50 
miles to the base it automaticly comes up. To long rrange scan can cover 
anywhere on the world. Just look for a certain signature. Say pred or 
maximal. Every bot thats outside of thier base will show up."
